---
import Container from "../../primitives/Container.astro";
---
<section class="bg-white" aria-labelledby="integrated-intro-title">
  <Container>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Why integrated systems</p>
      <h2 id="integrated-intro-title" class="fluid-h2 mt-3">Complex infrastructure requires more than standalone components.</h2>
      <p class="fluid-lead mt-5 text-muted">
        Empereal designs and delivers fully integrated architectural solar solutions that combine Building-Integrated Photovoltaics (BIPV), energy storage, smart controls, and thermal systems into one seamless, high-performance building envelope.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-muted leading-relaxed">
        From iconic solar façades and net-zero buildings to integrated resorts and industrial facilities, we provide complete system integration — architectural design, structural engineering, electrical integration, and long-term O&amp;M — from a single specialized partner.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
